20
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:38,380
The place: the region of the Lake Biwa.
The time: end of the 16th century

21
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,620
What's this noise?

22
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:16,300
Spies, probably.

23
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:21,300
It's necessary that I have this
before the fight begins.

24
00:03:21,550 --> 00:03:23,620
Can you sell everything in Nagahama?

25
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:28,220
Yes. Hashiba's army arrival
brought prosperity.

26
00:03:28,990 --> 00:03:30,060
Shall I come with you?

27
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:34,900
No! These soldiers
are without mercy for the women.

28
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:39,700
Besides who would take care of
Genitchi, our son?

29
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:45,980
You are stupid,
to dream such a thing!

30
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:48,100
The ambition, as the ocean...

31
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,780
must be without limits!

32
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:55,460
You a Samurai..?
You don't even know how to fight!

33
00:03:56,790 --> 00:03:59,620
Continue working with my brother.

34
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:03,220
You will see!
In the name of the War god!

35
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:08,150
I have had enough, of misery!
I'll come with you.

36
00:04:08,350 --> 00:04:10,860
Stop thinking about these madness.

37
00:04:11,510 --> 00:04:12,620
I'll pull your cart.

38
00:04:13,390 --> 00:04:14,140
Be reasonable.

39
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:18,380
No, my brother. He believes that glory
awaits him in in the city.

40
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,420
He is stupid!

41
00:04:44,470 --> 00:04:49,780
They are mad, with their ideas,
Tobei Genjuro!

42
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:55,820
The so easily won money
fly off quickly.

43
00:04:56,950 --> 00:05:00,340
It overexcites
the imbecile desires!

44
00:05:01,350 --> 00:05:04,780
The war approaches.
They'd better prepare for it.

45
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:10,180
Say that to Genjuro.

46
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:24,180
Here's Dad coming home!

47
00:05:34,150 --> 00:05:36,020
Look at that!

48
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,060
Can you imagine!

49
00:05:41,230 --> 00:05:42,870
What a beautiful profit!

50
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:49,540
I came back in hurry,
to show it to you.

51
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:56,820
That's what i call trade!
Do you understand?

52
00:06:01,710 --> 00:06:02,820
And Tobeï?

53
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:06,270
He followed a great Samurai,

54
00:06:06,470 --> 00:06:10,430
Despite my advice.

55
00:06:45,910 --> 00:06:50,700
Lord! Take me to your service.
I am brave.

56
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:54,740
Go away filthy beggar !

57
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,460
you would need an
armor.
And a spear.

58
00:06:58,150 --> 00:07:00,380
And I could be a Samurai?

59
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,500
You are still there?

60
00:07:15,990 --> 00:07:17,580
And your armor?

61
00:07:28,110 --> 00:07:31,700
You are splendid ! Are you happy?

62
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:35,700
You are superb!

63
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:42,740
You make me so happy !

64
00:07:45,910 --> 00:07:50,460
For years, I wanted
to buy you pretty things.

65
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:53,340
Finally, my dream
comes true.

66
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:58,140
I am so happy
to see you happy!

67
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:01,740
It is not because of the kimono...

68
00:08:02,150 --> 00:08:04,620
but because of your love.

69
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:12,700
My only desire is to keep you close to me.

70
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:22,660
I also brought some supplies.

71
00:08:23,350 --> 00:08:28,500
Smoked Fish... oil...
flour... rice cakes!

72
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:36,620
Without money, there is only misery.
And hope dies!

73
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:43,740
I want to bring back even more money!

74
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:49,340
I will work harder...

75
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:59,620
I will make masses of potteries!

76
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:03,660
Stop for now, Genjuro.

77
00:09:04,070 --> 00:09:09,140
The chief of the village announces
the arrival of the Shibata army.

78
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,950
Stay home.

79
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:14,260
Stupid! The war is good for trade.

80
00:09:14,470 --> 00:09:15,700
See that beautiful profit!

81
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:20,020
And if luck abandodonned you?

82
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:22,980
If something happened to you ..?

83
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:25,060
don't worry!

84
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:26,940
Here... Ohama!

85
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:28,860
My brother!

86
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:31,340
don't torment him.

87
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:35,100
No Samurai will hire
a poor peasant.

88
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:40,020
He will qickly come back!
Let's have a hot drink.

89
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:54,300
Idiot! Do you understand..?

90
00:09:55,110 --> 00:10:00,340
Look at you...
the silliest of the whole village!

91
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,510
You can spin!

92
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:29,020
Send him away,
he embarrasses us.

93
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:33,740
Behave yourself, my boy.

94
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:37,900
Mom... I am hungry!

95
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:43,870
He irritates me!.. Let's go, spin!

96
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,860
You change so much!

97
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:54,060
You become irate.

98
00:10:54,870 --> 00:10:59,260
I only want a thing:
to work together.

99
00:11:00,310 --> 00:11:03,380
All three.

100
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:06,620
nothing else matters.

101
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:41,460
You work hard!

102
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:43,860
because I have a plan.

103
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:52,620
We will go to Nagahama.
And we will become rich!

104
00:11:53,230 --> 00:11:54,630
I will have a share?

105
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:57,830
Of course! A third of the sale.

106
00:11:58,390 --> 00:12:02,020
I need money so much!

107
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:12,030
I never saw them working like that.

108
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:17,510
They live only for this oven.

109
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:22,300
Bodies and soul! both of them.

110
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:28,340
If it fails,
what will they become?

111
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:32,380
what he has should be enough.

112
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:35,310
But no!

113
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:41,460
He was so quiet, until now!

114
00:12:41,950 --> 00:12:44,590
War changes people so much!

115
00:12:45,070 --> 00:12:47,980
don't antagonize them.

116
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,140
Listen!

117
00:12:56,430 --> 00:12:58,540
Stand up, Genjuro!

118
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:05,420
That must be the Shibata army!

119
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:16,860
Tobeï, what's happening?

120
00:13:17,310 --> 00:13:19,700
All the neighbors run away!

121
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:22,420
What shall we do?

122
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:24,580
the fire... It's going to die out...

123
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:27,550
It must not!

124
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:30,750
They arrive!
They are going to strip us!

125
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:35,460
Genitchi!..

126
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:12,580
The Shibata army is there!

127
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:16,420
The Shibata army... Run!

128
00:14:20,270 --> 00:14:23,150
They will take the men!

129
00:14:26,350 --> 00:14:29,420
If they had only arrived tomorrow!

130
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:33,980
Let's go, quickly, there is danger!

131
00:14:35,470 --> 00:14:37,300
My fortune is in this oven!

132
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:45,860
But your life is lot more precious!

133
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:52,580
Take some rice! We will need
it in the mountain.

134
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:56,020
Ohama... Quickly!

135
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,860
Help..!

136
00:15:33,230 --> 00:15:36,620
Spare our men,
or we will die of hunger!

137
00:16:52,190 --> 00:16:54,180
Here, it's cooked.

138
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:58,780
We can eat.

139
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,940
What's happenning?

140
00:17:03,510 --> 00:17:04,780
This Tobeï! What an idiot !

141
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,780
Didd you saw my husband?

142
00:17:13,230 --> 00:17:14,980
No, nowhere.

143
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:46,340
Who's there..?

144
00:18:03,870 --> 00:18:06,510
Everything has calmed down

145
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:08,860
We can't hear a thing.

146
00:18:20,990 --> 00:18:22,260
Genjuros, where are you going..?

147
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:26,060
Patience!
They won't remain here long.

148
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:28,110
You'd better wait.

149
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:30,700
I can't, I have to leave.

150
00:18:31,150 --> 00:18:33,900
We will be ruined!

151
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:36,620
Sacrify the batch!..
And if you were taken?

152
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:38,940
We can't let it die out!

153
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:42,700
We'll start again. Later!

154
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:45,540
I don't want to abandon my oven!

155
00:19:06,630 --> 00:19:08,860
It died out!

156
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:21,780
No more hope.

157
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:39,700
Some must hide there.

158
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:43,660
Let's search everywhere!

159
00:20:02,990 --> 00:20:04,550
Nothing but pots!

160
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:38,110
They are cooked!

161
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:42,500
Look... they are finished!

162
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,150
They are saved?

163
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:56,670
Yes, all cooked. Thanks Heaven!

164
00:20:58,870 --> 00:21:00,270
Then, we return to the city?

165
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:03,660
This time, we will cross the lake.

166
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:07,220
Ohama is a good rower.
Let her come.

167
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:09,620
Can we arrive?

168
00:21:10,390 --> 00:21:12,180
Yes, by taking a shortcut.

169
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:13,940
And the boat?

170
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:17,860
We will surely find one on the beach.

171
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:56,590
Careful, the fog is thick.

172
00:22:59,230 --> 00:23:01,740
Genitchi, do you see the lake?

173
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:02,940
It is pretty.

174
00:23:04,590 --> 00:23:06,580
Finally, out of danger!

175
00:23:07,910 --> 00:23:10,470
Glad that we go there by water.

176
00:23:11,390 --> 00:23:14,140
By the fields, we could have been killed.

177
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,420
In the morning, we will be in Omizo...

178
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:20,420
Where the castle of
the Lord Niwa is.

179
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:23,740
It is a much bigger city
than Nagahama.

180
00:23:24,470 --> 00:23:26,900
We will be rich!

181
00:23:27,470 --> 00:23:30,540
And our wives too!

182
00:23:32,990 --> 00:23:35,870
I will have a
vast warehouse built.

183
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,820
I will buy an armor!

184
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:10,510
Look... a boat!

185
00:24:22,710 --> 00:24:23,900
A ghost!

186
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:27,860
No, I am not a ghost.

187
00:24:29,710 --> 00:24:32,270
But a fisher, from Kaïzu.

188
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:41,260
I have been attacked by pirates
while going... to Azuchi.

189
00:24:42,830 --> 00:24:46,870
Water... please!

190
00:25:07,830 --> 00:25:11,710
Wherever you go
watch out for the pirates!

191
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:16,220
They'll take your life...

192
00:25:16,870 --> 00:25:18,940
and your goods...

193
00:25:20,990 --> 00:25:22,060
and especially your women!

194
00:25:38,430 --> 00:25:39,180
Buddha has his soul!

195
00:25:52,870 --> 00:25:56,780
Let's go back home.
The danger is too big.

196
00:26:00,870 --> 00:26:03,940
Let put the women ashore.
We will go alone.

197
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:07,860
I go there, to supervise you.

198
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:08,940
You will be kidnapped!

199
00:26:09,390 --> 00:26:10,500
I'll take the risk.

200
00:26:10,710 --> 00:26:13,620
Please, take me with you.

201
00:26:13,990 --> 00:26:15,780
Think about our kid.

202
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:20,820
Turn around, Ohama... Faster!

203
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:45,780
We will come back money.
Before 10 days.

204
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:53,780
May the gods protect you!

205
00:26:54,790 --> 00:27:00,260
Avoid the road,
take the mountain trails.

206
00:27:00,710 --> 00:27:02,430
Stay away of the villages.

207
00:27:03,110 --> 00:27:07,260
These misfortunes won't last.
Patience!

208
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:12,540
Be  careful all of you!

209
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:17,380
See you soon!

210
00:27:18,230 --> 00:27:19,710
Take good care of Genitchi!

211
00:27:19,990 --> 00:27:21,780
We will bring back a lot of money!

212
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:24,190
Dad!

213
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,340
Good luck!..

214
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:09,820
I will take this vase.

215
00:29:14,190 --> 00:29:17,220
And this sake pot, and these two bowls.

216
00:29:21,230 --> 00:29:25,900
These rice bowls and these plates.
And these pots.

217
00:29:27,790 --> 00:29:31,180
Rice bowls, plates and pots.

218
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:33,900
We live in the Manor Kutsuki,
on the mountain.

219
00:29:34,350 --> 00:29:36,260
Deliver them there.

220
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:39,940
We will pay you then.

221
00:29:40,430 --> 00:29:43,100
Thank you, Madame..
Very well.

222
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:59,700
The Castle's guard! Make place!

223
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:15,540
I could be a samurai,
with an armor and a spear!

224
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:18,380
don't waste our money.

225
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:10,460
Do I look like a samurai?

226
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:14,820
Certainly!
But you need a spear.

227
00:31:31,630 --> 00:31:33,660
You are superb!

228
00:33:26,990 --> 00:33:28,140
Your salary!

229
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:07,780
Idiot!..

230
00:34:11,030 --> 00:34:14,340
You see it, my misfortune..?

231
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:18,580
thanks to you,
your wife is reduced to that!

232
00:34:20,270 --> 00:34:23,700
Be proud to have become a Samurai
at such a price!

233
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:27,300
Tobeï... Big fool..!

234
00:34:58,510 --> 00:35:01,660
Would you watch over my stall?

235
00:35:02,790 --> 00:35:04,660
My partner is coming back.

236
00:35:33,270 --> 00:35:35,260
How much is it..?

237
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:39,020
Do you want to buy it?

238
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:41,700
If the price is right.

239
00:35:42,350 --> 00:35:45,980
It is much too beautiful
for your wife!

240
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:47,900
But I have the money!

241
00:36:49,350 --> 00:36:53,420
We thought
that it was better to guide you.

242
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:56,870
You are so good!

243
00:37:01,750 --> 00:37:03,100
Follow us!

244
00:38:26,550 --> 00:38:27,900
Move on!

245
00:38:29,390 --> 00:38:33,380
Thank you, but I would like...

246
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:37,460
Dame Wakasa wants to
see you.

247
00:38:39,270 --> 00:38:42,660
That is the princess's name?

248
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:46,860
She is the unique daughter
of the late Lord Kutsuki.

249
00:38:47,310 --> 00:38:50,820
Do not fear... Enter!

250
00:41:04,110 --> 00:41:06,500
Comwith me.

251
00:41:17,550 --> 00:41:21,980
You are indeed Master Genjuro,
from the province of Ohmi?

252
00:41:25,590 --> 00:41:28,230
How do you know it?

253
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:34,220
At the  market,
when I saw your ceramics...

254
00:41:35,110 --> 00:41:37,750
I hardly believed my eyes!

255
00:41:38,430 --> 00:41:41,230
These blue reflections seemed...

256
00:41:41,430 --> 00:41:44,540
to be made of mother of pearl!

257
00:41:46,430 --> 00:41:48,820
thanks to the lessons
taught by my father...

258
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:51,980
I am able to appreciate them.

259
00:41:53,870 --> 00:41:59,820
How do you create such beauty!

260
00:42:01,230 --> 00:42:03,900
Do you have a secret?

261
00:42:05,950 --> 00:42:08,460
No special secret.

262
00:42:09,470 --> 00:42:14,780
kneading and varnishing
require a certain knack.

263
00:42:16,950 --> 00:42:21,540
what you realize
is a pure marvel!

264
00:42:22,150 --> 00:42:25,060
Only, a true master craftsman
can create such a beauty!

265
00:42:25,270 --> 00:42:26,140
Thank you, Madam..

266
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:57,220
But... these are my works!

267
00:43:00,630 --> 00:43:04,980
