so happy to see you back.

537
01:27:45,710 --> 01:27:50,300
Since her death,
I kept your child at home.

538
01:27:51,750 --> 01:27:54,550
I was so aafraid,
when he disappeared!

539
01:27:58,030 --> 01:28:00,670
The voice of blood, it is marvelous!

540
01:28:01,270 --> 01:28:05,060
How could he know that you were here!

541
01:28:31,630 --> 01:28:36,750
You didn't understand your madness
until meeting your misfortune.

542
01:28:37,230 --> 01:28:40,820
The war ruined all our hopes.

543
01:28:41,950 --> 01:28:44,830
Let my sacrifice not be vain.

544
01:28:45,430 --> 01:28:47,620
Be brave!..

545
01:29:08,550 --> 01:29:10,380
Why did you die?

546
01:29:32,870 --> 01:29:35,260
<i>I didn't die, my beloved.</i>

547
01:29:36,150 --> 01:29:38,820
<i>I am close to you.</i>

548
01:29:44,830 --> 01:29:47,300
<i>Your long road is to its end.</i>

549
01:29:47,790 --> 01:29:50,140
<i>Come back to your place.</i>

550
01:29:51,470 --> 01:29:54,220
<i>Take back your work...</i>

551
01:30:06,110 --> 01:30:09,460
<i>It is so pretty!</i>

552
01:30:11,430 --> 01:30:15,660
<i>Helping you is my greatest pleasure.</i>

553
01:30:19,550 --> 01:30:22,140
<i>I can't wait to see them finished.</i>

554
01:30:24,030 --> 01:30:26,180
<i>The logs are ready.</i>

555
01:30:27,310 --> 01:30:30,270
<i>Pillagers won't come anymore</i>

556
01:30:32,590 --> 01:30:34,980
<i>Spin your potteries in peace.</i>

557
01:30:40,670 --> 01:30:43,140
<i>A lot of things happened.</i>

558
01:30:45,910 --> 01:30:50,860
<i>But you became
The man of my ideal.</i>

559
01:30:52,190 --> 01:30:59,820
<i>Alas, I am not anymore 
in the same world than yours.</i>

560
01:31:02,030 --> 01:31:05,580
<i>We must resign...</i>

561
01:31:26,270 --> 01:31:28,830
You must be tired. Rest.

562
01:31:38,750 --> 01:31:42,380
Kid, eat while it's hot.

563
01:31:43,350 --> 01:31:45,420
You too, my brother!..

